g the same output format.\n./docs/DEVELOPING.md:324:- List available coordinates: `./gradlew listCoordinates -Pcoordinates=[group:artifact:version|group:artifact|k/n|all] [-PstrictCoordinates=true]`\n./build.gradle:148:            \"listCoordinates\",\n./build.gradle:262:    t.setDescription(\"Determines one artifact coordinate via generateInfrastructureChangedCoordinatesMatrix (or uses -Pcoordinate/-Pcoordinates if provided), then runs testInfra for that coordinate and also for 1/64. Options: -Pparallelism to control concurrency.\")\n./build.gradle:292:                throw new GradleException(\"No coordinates found in generateInfrastructureChangedCoordinatesMatrix output. Provide -Pcoordinate or -Pcoordinates to override.\")\n./build.gradle:334: * Runs generateInfrastructureChangedCoordinatesMatrix and returns the log file.\n./build.gradle:342:    def logFile = new File(logsDir, \"generateInfrastructureChangedCoordinatesMatrix.log\")\n./build.gradle:344:        [gradleCmd, \"generateInfrastructureChangedCoordinatesMatrix\"],\n./build.gradle:345:        \"generateInfrastructureChangedCoordinatesMatrix\",\n./ci.json:18:  \"generateInfrastructureChangedCoordinatesMatrix\": {\n./ci.json:32:  \"generateChangedMetadataTestMatrix\": {\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
